title: SPACIOUS UNIT IN REACH BRICKELL!!
posting_body: ['**Please note that the unit will be completely painted before new tenant move in.', 'Spacious 1 bedroom in The Reach Condominium, this unit offers it all.', 'Tremendous balcony overlooking the canal and Marlins Park.', 'Modern finishes.', 'Walking closets.', 'Convenient half bath.', 'Building offers the best amenities with gym, kids playground, pool and more.', 'Can beat this location in the heart of Brickell close to everything.', 'Easy to show', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
